WEBVTT

33:56.550 --> 33:57.440 line:80%
How about this?

33:57.720 --> 34:00.760 line:80%
You supply the braised meat to us
for the New Year first,

34:00.760 --> 34:04.070 line:80%
and I'll figure out a way to fill the gap
after the New Year.

34:05.590 --> 34:07.410 line:80%
You'll need to buy a new house
in a new place.
